{"word":"Ὀρτυγία","slug":"Ὀρτυγία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n75384\" key=\"*)ortugi/a\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">Ὀρτῠγία</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ιη,</foreign> <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen><foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">, (ὄρτυξ)</foreign> <sense id=\"n75384.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">Quail-island,</tr_> the ancient name of Delos or Rhenaea, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10:5:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10.5.5</biblScope> </bibl> ; also of other places in Greece ; in one of these Artemis killed <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Orion\">Orion</a></author></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:5:123\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.123</biblScope> </bibl>: hence she is called <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ὀρτυγία,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg001.perseus-grc1:213\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">213</biblScope> </bibl> (lyr.). </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n75384.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> part of the city of Syracuse, otherwise called <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Νᾶσος,</foreign> the Island, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:2:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.2.4</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}